sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API as FastAPI Gateway
    participant Adapter as Source Adapter
    participant Queue as ARQ Job Queue
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant Store as Storage

    rect rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.08)
        Note over User,Store: Phase 1 — Ingestion
        User->>+API: POST /ingest/url
        API->>+Adapter: Extract text + metadata
        Adapter->>Store: Save raw source file
        Adapter-->>-API: Source (status: ingested)
        API-->>-User: 201 Created + Source ID
    end

    rect rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.08)
        Note over User,Store: Phase 2 — Compilation (background)
        API->>+Queue: Schedule compile job
        Queue->>+LLM: Send source + system prompt
        LLM-->>-Queue: JSON (article + claims + concepts)
        Queue->>Store: Save article (.md + DB row)
        Queue->>Store: Upsert concepts + backlinks
        Queue-->>-API: Job complete
        API-->>User: WebSocket: compilation.complete
    end

    rect rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.08)
        Note over User,Store: Phase 3 — Query
        User->>+API: POST /query
        API->>Store: Retrieve relevant articles
        API->>+LLM: Q&A with wiki context
        LLM-->>-API: Answer + citations
        API-->>-User: QueryResult (streamed)
    end
